{
  "stem": "4272.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Juden-- no, there was not a Judenrat yet, but they would have a complete list of all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't think that there was a regis--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Is this what the Germans used then?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They probably used that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I can't say for sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you say that a ghetto was formed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was there a wall?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were guards, and there were two points where we could-- actually, nobody was allowed to leave, but for the Germans to come in and out more.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for the Polish police, that they could come into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But otherwise, we were not allowed to go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What nationality were the guards?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time, German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was before the war brought in the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was your father able to work?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He worked for the-- for the Germans, because when they found out that he's such a fine cabinet-maker, furniture-maker, they wanted him to make some things for them, which he did.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were so happy with him-- so pleased-- that one German told him, don't worry, you'll be the last Jew to be killed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, he didn't leave him any hope right away in the beginning that he's going to save him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He just assured him that he'll be the last Jew to be killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What about food?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where you able to have enough food?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While-- while in the ghetto, you mean?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Plozk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, at first it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At first, we-- we could find food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Were you able to take all your belongings with you when you went into the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because they put in three, four families into maybe a three-room apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
